info: ***1st DOSE PFIZER VACCINATIONS!!!!***!!!!VACUNAS DE PRIMERA DOSIS PFIZER!!! SELAH CIVIC CENTER!!! Masks are required. Please wear clothing which allows access to your shoulder.
